## 10. DB 表设计

### 10.1 通用 Agent 任务表：`agent_tasks`

```sql
CREATE TABLE agent_tasks (
    id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT,

    task_id VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    task_type VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
    agent_name VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,

    subject_type VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
    subject_id VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,

    source_agent VARCHAR(64) NULL,
    source_task_id VARCHAR(64) NULL,

    status VARCHAR(32) NOT NULL,
    -- CREATED / RUNNING / COMPLETED / FAILED / HANDOFF_CREATED

    payload_json JSON NOT NULL,
    result_json JSON NULL,
    error_message TEXT NULL,

    created_at DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,

    INDEX idx_agent_tasks_subject (subject_type, subject_id),
    INDEX idx_agent_tasks_agent (agent_name),
    INDEX idx_agent_tasks_status (status)
);
```

---

### 10.2 审核单表：`review_cases`

```sql
CREATE TABLE review_cases (
